British-Libyan surgeon and humanitarian who writes under the pen name Amal Al-
Leebi went nostalgic and published some old pictures from previous visits to
Libya on his Twitter account,
@[libyansrevolt](http://twitter.com/libyansrevolt/), to show the Libya he
remembers.

